- [UX Collective — Date Picker Design](https://uxdesign.cc/date-picker-design-5c5ef8f35286)
- [Smashing Magazine — Designing the Perfect Date/Time Picker](https://www.smashingmagazine.com/2017/07/designing-perfect-date-time-picker/)
- [Glide Community — Time-of-day greeting](https://community.glideapps.com/t/personalized-user-greeting-based-on-time-of-day/74101)
